OL,3,CTitanic and The Lord of the Rings
OL,4,Cactor Bernard Hill dies aged 79
OL,6,FActor Bernard Hill, best known for his
OL,7,Froles in Titanic and The Lord of the
OL,8,FRings trilogy, has died aged 79, his
OL,9,Fagent confirmed.
OL,11,FHill's agent, Lou Coulson, told the PA
OL,12,Fnews agency that he died in the early
OL,13,Fhours of Sunday.
OL,15,FThe actor played Captain Edward Smith
OL,16,Fin the Oscar-winning 1997 epic romance
OL,17,FTitanic, which starred Leonardo
OL,18,FDiCaprio and Kate Winslet.
