OL,3,CTitanic and The Lord of the Rings
OL,4,Cactor Bernard Hill dies aged 79
OL,6,FHe also portrayed Theoden, King of
OL,7,FRohan, in The Lord Of The Rings
OL,8,Ftrilogy directed by Sir Peter Jackson.
OL,10,FHill joined the Lord Of The Rings cast
OL,11,Ffor the second film in the trilogy,
OL,12,F2002's The Two Towers, which won two
OL,13,FAcademy Awards for best sound editing
OL,14,Fand best visual effects.
OL,16,FHe returned to the franchise for
OL,17,F2003's The Return Of The King, which
OL,18,Fpicked up 11 Oscars, including best
OL,19,Fpicture and best director for Sir
OL,20,FPeter.
