OL,6,FHill also starred in drama series Boys
OL,7,FFrom The Blackstuff, and the 2015 BBC
OL,8,Fadaptation of Hilary Mantel's novel
OL,9,FWolf Hall.
OL,11,FThe BBC described him as an
OL,12,F"incredible talent" who "blazed a
OL,13,Ftrail across the screen" during his
OL,14,Fcareer.
OL,16,FActress and musician Barbara Dickson,
OL,17,Fwho starred with him in a musical
OL,18,Fbased on the Beatles, was among those
OL,19,Fpaying tribute, describing him as a
OL,20,F"marvellous actor".
